<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM5.3">
<l>mātali tērmuṉpu kōlkoḷḷa māyaṉi rāvaṇaṉ mēṟcara māri</l>
<l>tāytalai yaṟṟaṟṟu vīḻat toṭutta talaivaṉ varaveṅkuṅ kāṇēṉ</l>
<l>pōtalar kāviṟ putumaṇam nāṟap poṟivaṇṭiṉ kāmaraṅ kēṭṭuṉ</l>
<l>kātali yōṭuṭaṉ vāḻkuyi lēyeṉ karumāṇik kamvarak kūvāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I do not see the Lord—who dispatched showers of arrows on the deceitful Rāvaṇa</l>
<l rend="indent">as Mātali drove with a whip in hand in front of [Rāvaṇa’s] chariot,</l>
<l>so that [his] main head fell severed again and again—come anywhere!</l>
<l>O cuckoo that live along with your beloved listening to the kāmaram musical mode</l>
<l rend="indent">of the spotted bees</l>
<l>as a new fragrance is emitted in the grove where flowers bloom!</l>
<l rend="indent">Cry so that my Dark Sapphire comes!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
